@startuml
mainframe **sd** DetailReport
hide footbox

actor "**: User**" as User
boundary "**: DetailReportPage**" as DetailReportPage
control "**: TestController**" as TestController
entity "**: TestCaseRepository**" as TestCaseRepository

User -> DetailReportPage : selectTestCase(testCaseID)
activate DetailReportPage

DetailReportPage -> TestController : fetchTestDetails(testCaseID)
activate TestController

TestController -> TestCaseRepository : getTestByID(testCaseID)
activate TestCaseRepository

' Koreksi Mistake 3.21 & 3.11: Menggunakan pesan balasan (-->) dengan nilai
TestCaseRepository --> TestController : testData
deactivate TestCaseRepository

TestController --> DetailReportPage : testData
deactivate TestController
@enduml